  "notes": [
    "This bundle is repo-owned and intentionally clean-room.",
    "It materializes a first complete-run tracker surface without copying third-party tracker runtime code.",
    "Licensed static assets and JSON data from the pinned PopTracker pack are included under poptracker-adapted/ with provenance and license.",
    "It embeds repo-owned location groups, item slots, dungeon progress, room metadata, and data-driven tracker flow instructions directly in the bundle archive.",
    "Item icons, map pins, settings rendering, and autotabbing hints are declared as data-only metadata for Sekaiemu consumption."
